Hey guys!  Well this was my second script that I posted a LONG LONG time ago.  And various people have requested that I update it, so I have.  ;D

Remember that jagex only allows you to create 5 accounts every 30 minutes or something like that.  So I don't really see a need in an account creator anymore, but you guys demanded lol.  

This took me hardly no time at all to completely redo the entire script, and it is pretty simple, yet effective.  So don't get mad if it messes up(which it shouldn't) because I know this is not the best out there :P
Just simply report the error to me in this thread.

This doesn't have a failsafe for if that account has already been chosen. Maybe I will add if you guys want?

Please post any bugs, improvements you want, thanks? , or whatever.

NOTE: [i]This does not do tutorial island, it only creates accounts![/i]

And last but not least the script.  Copy and paste into SCAR then follow the scripts directions.
